			<a href="https://panopticlick.eff.org/" class="btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Browser Fingerprint by EFF</a>
			<a href="https://raymondhill.net/ublock/tiles1.html" class="btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Adblock Testing by raymondhill</a>
			<a href="https://raymondhill.net/ublock/popup.html" class="btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Popup Blocker by raymondhill</a>
